OL,5, Walkers wanting to enjoy footpaths     
OL,6, across the British countryside are     
OL,7, being blocked or obstructed in nearly  
OL,8, 32,000 places across England and Wales.
OL,10,FBut they are fighting back, with one   
OL,11,Frambler even training as a lawyer to   
OL,12,Fforce councils to keep the way clear.  
OL,14,FA BBC investigation found councils     
OL,15,Fwhich have responsibility for footpaths
OL,16,Fhad 4,000 more access issues on public 
OL,17,Frights of way in 2023 than in 2022.    
OL,19,FCampaigners said this showed a "growing
OL,20,Fabuse and neglect" of the path network.
